title: Hubby's lover to flip evidence in case of missing mom of 5 Jennifer Dulos?
itunes:title: Hubby's lover to flip evidence in case of missing mom of 5 Jennifer Dulos?
description:
The body of missing mom of five, Jennifer Dulos, has not been found. But both her estranged husband and his girlfriend have been arrested for a second time. Now it seems Michelle Troconis is rolling over on Fotis Dulos, telling police she cannot provide him an alibi. With Nancy Grace today to discuss the impact of this new information on the case is: Former Assistant District Attorney and now defense attorney Darryl Cohen, Karen Smith Forensics Expert with Bare Bones Consulting, and RadarOnline Entertainment Editor Alexis Terezchuck.
